{"words":[{"word":"people","count":4},{"word":"ragunna","count":3},{"word":"order","count":3},{"word":"must","count":2},{"word":"singing","count":2},{"word":"truth","count":2},{"word":"knights","count":2},{"word":"te","count":2},{"word":"call","count":2},{"word":"something","count":2},{"word":"banish","count":2},{"word":"rimbaud","count":1},{"word":"selena","count":1},{"word":"returned","count":1},{"word":"lithograph","count":1},{"word":"sentinel's","count":1},{"word":"true","count":1},{"word":"form","count":1},{"word":"somewhere","count":1},{"word":"gentleman","count":1},{"word":"guide","count":1},{"word":"intentionally","count":1},{"word":"exactly","count":1},{"word":"backpack","count":1},{"word":"stuffed","count":1},{"word":"papers","count":1},{"word":"claiming","count":1},{"word":"common","count":1},{"word":"artist","count":1},{"word":"traveling","count":1},{"word":"search","count":1},{"word":"inspiration","count":1},{"word":"yet","count":1},{"word":"spoke","count":1},{"word":"nobleman","count":1},{"word":"afford","count":1},{"word":"help","count":1},{"word":"praises","count":1},{"word":"false","count":1},{"word":"sentinel","count":1},{"word":"cannot","count":1},{"word":"continue","count":1},{"word":"sing","count":1},{"word":"anymore","count":1},{"word":"enlighten","count":1},{"word":"deserve","count":1},{"word":"defend","count":1},{"word":"order's","count":1},{"word":"interests","count":1},{"word":"time","count":1},{"word":"become","count":1},{"word":"allow","count":1},{"word":"share","count":1},{"word":"answer","count":1},{"word":"sir","count":1},{"word":"acolyte","count":1},{"word":"remember","count":1},{"word":"first","count":1},{"word":"voice","count":1},{"word":"heavens","count":1},{"word":"rinascita","count":1},{"word":"kept","count":1},{"word":"alive","count":1},{"word":"hearts","count":1},{"word":"built","count":1},{"word":"homes","count":1},{"word":"land","count":1},{"word":"surely","count":1},{"word":"seen","count":1},{"word":"href","count":1},{"word":"golden","count":1},{"word":"bough","count":1},{"word":"yes","count":1},{"word":"play","count":1},{"word":"various","count":1},{"word":"clans","count":1},{"word":"wear","count":1},{"word":"masks","count":1},{"word":"celebrating","count":1},{"word":"together","count":1},{"word":"occasion","count":1},{"word":"carnevale","count":1},{"word":"words","count":1},{"word":"songs","count":1},{"word":"enemies","count":1},{"word":"face","count":1},{"word":"hard","count":1},{"word":"describe","count":1},{"word":"reverberation","count":1},{"word":"exists","count":1},{"word":"forever","count":1},{"word":"never","count":1},{"word":"defeat","count":1},{"word":"deep","count":1},{"word":"seeks","count":1},{"word":"seas","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Rimbaud and Selena must have returned to Ragunna by now. That lithograph of the Sentinel's true form… it has to be here somewhere.","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"Did that gentleman guide us intentionally? Who exactly was he...","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"Backpack stuffed with papers, claiming to be a common artist traveling in search of inspiration.","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"Yet he spoke like a nobleman... But I can't afford to think about that now.","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"If not for his help, we'd still be singing praises to a false Sentinel!","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"He's right. We cannot continue to sing for the Order anymore.","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"We must enlighten the people of Ragunna. They deserve to know the truth.","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"The knights of the Order defend only the Order's interests, and so... the time has come for us to become knights for the people of Ragunna.","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"Allow me to share the answer, Sir Acolyte. Do you remember the very first voice from the heavens? The one the people of Rinascita kept alive in their hearts as they built their homes on this land?","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"Surely you've seen <te href=800009>The Golden Bough</te>, yes? A play where people from various clans wear masks, singing and celebrating together. An occasion you now call... \"Carnevale.\"","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"It is words and songs. We are not your enemies. What you face here is something that is hard to describe, something I call \"Reverberation.\"","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"It exists forever, and you can never defeat it.","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003},{"text":"The Order of the Deep seeks to banish us to the seas because they know they can't banish the truth...","quest_name":"Your Summer Will Never Wither","quest_id":165000003}]}